2016-03-25 12-00-00:
	Title: Registrations for Red Alert: Global League now open!
	Author: Oliver Brakmann
	Content: Our well-known community member and caster SoScared is organizing a Red Alert: Global League.\n\nThere will be at least two divisions of 12 players each competing for the top spots in the tables. As with the recent Tag Team Tournament, there will again be a prize pool, to be distributed among the top players. RA:GL will run from April 4th until June 19th 2016. For more details and in-depth information, visit the forum thread at http://forum.openra.net/82/19512. Registrations are open until March 30th, 0:00 UTC.\n\nWe wish all participants the best of luck and a lot of fun!
